Memimi-chan is just so cute. And this one, where she's
getting fucked by a customer... it's just irresistible!

Memimi: Aaaaah... no, no way...! They're selling my
embarrassing videos... This is too cruel... In the store
where I work, they're selling such things...

Orca Asparagus-Mayor: The main sales of your videos come
from the subscription-based erotic video streaming sites,
but those with poor connections or without credit cards buy
the packaged or downloadable versions. Of course, we're
wholesaling not just here but to real stores nationwide!

Orca Asparagus-Mayor: Now, since it's a special occasion,

Memimi: Raw... no, that's... I don't want to... it's a
lie... what kind of joke is this...? Eek... doing such a
